title: "R SuperLearner analysis"
format: html
---

```{r}
set.seed(123)
library(SuperLearner)
library(randomForest)
X <- as.data.frame(matrix(rnorm(500*10), nrow=500))
Y <- rbinom(500, 1, 0.5)
SL.library <- c("SL.randomForest", "SL.glm")

fit <- SuperLearner(Y=Y, X=X, SL.library=SL.library, method="method.NNloglik", cvControl = list(V = 5))
print(fit)
```
